  "title": "V2 Documentation",
  "body": "This issue tracks the different tasks to do in order to release the v2 of instantsearch.js\r\n\r\n - [x] Integrate documentationjs in the documentation pipeline (metalsmith)\r\n - [x] Read and generate pages for connectors\r\n - [x] Read and generate pages for widgets\r\n - [x] Read and generate pages for commons (instantsearch, basic structures like widget and connectors)\r\n - [x] Landing page\r\n - [x] integrate examples + pimp with advanced features (SFFV, show more)\r\n - [x] Create connectors guide\r\n - [x] Create upgrade to v2 guide\r\n - [x] publishable in /v2 (update v1 doc to notify of the v2)?\r\n\r\nThe [new documentation](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/) is available.",
